@victoriayue  Sorry to hear you're having trouble installing Ludwig.  To be able to assist you, I need a better understanding of the situation.
* You write about installing Ludwig v0.1.0.  The current release of Ludwig is v0.3.3.  Is there a reason you're installing an older version?
* You identify the OS as MacOS Big Sur.  I just want to confirm the hardware platform.  Is your Mac based on the Intel processor or Apple's new M1 ARM processor?  The reason I ask is there are known issues, beyond our control, for running Ludwig on the M1 ARM processor at this time.
